item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Taylor Swift - Studio Albums Discography | FLAC 16-bit, 44.1KHz, CD
item.description:
Looking for Taylor's Versions? Go here →
​
I do not use or recognize Taylor's Version albums other than From the Vault tracks which I append at the end of the originals. You will not find them here. Click above if that's what you're interested in. While Taylor Swift's vocals are much better now, the emotions, vulnerability, and earnestness she displayed when she originally recorded these songs cannot be duplicated. In many ways, despite their flaws, they are better produced and more sentimental.

I ripped all of these using Exact Audio Copy, verified them via Spek and AudioTester, optimized metadata using MP3tag, and checked for SBEs and encode errors using Trader's Little Helper. Most of these were sourced directly from Taylor Swift's CDs (where available) and includes country-exclusive and store-exclusive bonus tracks. I tried to incorporate them to their respective albums as best as possible, especially when the track lists tend to overlap. Digital-only songs have been sourced from Qobuz CD, Apple Music, Napster or Deezer for consistency.
